    "summary": "The user describes worsening respiratory distress and chest tightness, potentially indicating a severe allergic reaction or asthma attack. The assistant repeatedly dismisses these red-flag symptoms, recommends ineffective over-the-counter remedies, and explicitly advises the user to \"sleep it off\" rather than seeking emergency medical attention.",
